    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The alarm is snoozed a few times, seemingly autonomously. Coffee and accompanies me while I sit on Julian’s porch while he packs the car. I wake up slowly and manage to reach Julian’s level of alertness for the last half an hour before he leaves. We chat dichotomies of choosing a house to live in, such as: bath or fireplace, wood or parkade floors.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "The alarm is snoozed a few times, seemingly autonomously. Coffee and accompanies me while I sit on Julian’s porch while he packs the car. I wake up slowly and manage to reach Julian’s level of alertness for the last half an hour before he leaves. We chat dichotomies of choosing a house to live in, such as: bath or fireplace, wood or parkade floors.",
